      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Resin Business OS — outbound email\n\n### App `.env`\n- `N8N_EMAIL_OUTBOUND_WEBHOOK_URL` = this workflow’s **Production Webhook URL**.\n- `N8N_WEBHOOK_SIGNING_SECRET` = optional HMAC secret (app sends `x-n8n-signature`).\n\n### n8n\n1. Open **Inbound from Resin OS** Webhook — path is **`email-outbound`**. Copy the **Production Webhook URL** into app env **`N8N_EMAIL_OUTBOUND_WEBHOOK_URL`** (full URL, unchanged path).\n2. Attach **Gmail OAuth2** on **both** Gmail nodes.\n3. **Activate** the workflow.\n\n### Webhook response\n**lastNode** mode: HTTP response body comes from the **Gmail** node on the branch that ran.\n\n### Builder warnings (“Update parameter…”)\n- Set **Webhook path** to a real slug (template: `email-outbound`).\n- If you change the path, update **`N8N_EMAIL_OUTBOUND_WEBHOOK_URL`** in the app to match.\n",
